      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><ol>
<li>登录FCoin账户</li>
<li>依次点击【设置】--【安全设置】--【设置】<img src="/hc/article_attachments/360021155634/____1.png" alt="____1.png"></li>
<li>输入两次资金密码(六位数字)，点击【提交】</li>
</ol>
<p>        <img src="/hc/article_attachments/360022082313/____2.png" alt="____2.png"></p>
<p>   4.拖动滑块完成拼图</p>
<p>       <img src="/hc/article_attachments/360021155654/____3.png" alt="____3.png"></p>
<p>  5. 输入谷歌验证码或系统发送的邮箱验证码或者短信验证码，并点击【确认】，最终完成设置资金密码。</p>
<p>      <img src="/hc/article_attachments/360022082333/____4.png" alt="____4.png"></p></div>

